{"tid":1801664,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《新倚天屠龍記》演員名單曝光！傳古天樂林峯接這兩角色","createTime":"2019-12-28T20:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T10:48:46.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8baf6530034d5b2110e6367520944d3d5bfa2cbc","tid":1801664,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T20:04:40.000Z","msg":"《新倚天屠龍記》演員名單曝光！傳古天樂林峯接這兩角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-04-07/656/20190407002325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-04-07%2F656%2F20190407002325.jpg&h=44055bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經典電影《倚天屠龍記之魔教教主》當年由香港知名導演王晶執導，加上李連杰、張敏、邱淑貞、吳鎮宇、洪金寶等大咖巨星演出，在電影台播放數千次成為經典港片，時隔26年王晶宣布將拍攝2020年版本，「張無忌終於去大都找趙敏了」，網路上也瘋傳演員名單，甚至古天樂和林峯都將出演<br />\n<br />\n2020年版本的《倚天屠龍記》網傳演出名單包含張無忌由林峯飾演、古天樂飾張無忌父親張翠山，甄子丹則飾演張三豐、文詠珊飾演趙敏、徐錦江則再度接演演金毛獅王一角。<br />\n<br />\n不過這份名單並沒有被證實，導演王晶對演員名單也十分保密，這次的電影製作成本高達2億人民幣，這次的故事重點是張無忌去大都營救六派以及找張敏。"},{"pid":"013a6b340e1c6b25a4481f194b911df0af0ca6fe","tid":1801664,"uid":7206,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T20:25:48.000Z","msg":"王晶飾演白猿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4910f569f3afec2f9dc0c2151b1cf20ff7f83b19","tid":1801664,"uid":42509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8baf6530034d5b2110e6367520944d3d5bfa2cbc","tid":1801664,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T20:04:40.000Z","msg":"《新倚天屠龍記》演員名單曝光！傳古天樂林峯接這兩角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-04-07/656/20190407002325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-04-07%2F656%2F20190407002325.jpg&h=440